(720, 8, 'a_modern_workplace_', 'A Modern Workplace is a SAAS based online work environment that has been professionally designed to meet the needs of both your business and its employees. It utilizes the latest Microsoft technology to power and streamline business operations and empower employees to do their best work around the clock.'),
