(724, 8, 'microsoft_365_includes_description', 'Microsoft 365 includes Microsoft Power Automate, bringing the ability to use both Digital and Robotic Process Automation (RPA) across the business. This allows employees to focus on new ideas, instead of tedious tasks. With integrated AI capabilities and data integration with existing tools, you can quickly boost productivity for your company.'),
