(1928, 222, 'workplace_companion_develops', 'Workplace Companion develops and implements new ways to improve productivity. We can increase efficiency in the office by working with employees, assessing your IT infrastructure, develop goals, and outlining important improvements. Look at your workplace. Do employees have the resources they need to work well, including space, processes,\r\nand technologies? Beyond that, look at the cost. Is your business weighed down by massive overhead stemming from your lease? Are your facilities cost-efficient? '),
